title: Man accused of holding kidnapped woman in Oregon garage tried to escape from his jail cell, authorities say

title: Participants in California Tough Mudder event report rashes and fevers from bacterial infections
description: More than 100 people said they got bacterial infections after a Tough Mudder event in Sonoma, California. Symptoms included rashes, fever, muscle pain and vomiting.

title: Bronny James’ cardiac arrest was likely caused by a congenital heart defect, family says
description: LOS ANGELES — Bronny James' cardiac arrest and collapse during a workout were caused by a congenital heart defect that can be treated and won't keep him from basketball, a spokesperson for his family said.
